Package com.sun.identity.saml2.idpdiscovery

Interface IDPDiscoveryConstants

  • public interface IDPDiscoveryConstants
    This interface represents a collection of common constants used by the classes in saml2 idp discovery Service. Classes implementing this interface can use these constants.
